@startuml
actor User
participant "MainMenu" as Menu
participant "BudgetCalc" as Calc
database "CSV\n(budget.csv)" as DB

User -> Menu: 2. Добавить расход
Menu -> Calc: add_expense(amount, category, date)
Calc -> Calc: validate_amount(amount > 0)
alt превышен лимит
